        "timestamp": "2019-04-11 12:00:09.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\n(2 comments)\n\nI see, thanks Pam, see question below, just want to make sure everything looks fine when StandardCoder is not use in tandem, ie. encode/decode provided it is made the default.",
